description: Capitan Investment Ltd. engages in real estate development business in the United States. It focuses on the finance, development, operations, and property management of two real estate projects located in Amherst and Albany, New York. The company was formerly known as Sahara Energy Ltd. and changed its name to Capitan Investment Ltd. in December 2021. The company is headquartered in Calgary, Canada. Capitan Investment Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of JK Investment (Hong Kong) Co., Limited.
